branchCategory.name: C(D)QS, Compact Cylinder, Single Acting, Single Rod
branchCategory.description: <p>The CQS single rod, single acting version of the compact cylinder is available for those small bore cylinder applications where saving space is a concern. Both switch capable and non-switch capable body styles are the same, and switches can be mounted on three (12-16 bore) and four (20-25 bore) sides.</p>
